          howToUse: "<strong>Step 1:</strong> Open CapCut or InShot → New project.<br><strong>Step 2:</strong> Import your voice recording (even though there's no video, you can add a black background or an image).<br><strong>Step 3:</strong> Cut out mistakes: Split the audio at the mistake points and delete the bad sections.<br><strong>Step 4:</strong> Add background music: Import a music file or use the built-in library. Set volume to 15-20%.<br><strong>Step 5:</strong> Add fade in at the start and fade out at the end (for both voice and music).<br><strong>Step 6:</strong> Export as audio (or video with a static image). Some apps let you export audio-only."
