          howToUse: "<strong>Step 1:</strong> Go to forms.google.com → Click '+' to create a new form.<br><strong>Step 2:</strong> Settings (gear icon) → Enable 'Make this a quiz.'<br><strong>Step 3:</strong> Add your title and description.<br><strong>Step 4:</strong> Click '+' to add a question. Choose type: Multiple choice, checkboxes, short answer, etc.<br><strong>Step 5:</strong> Enter question text. Add answer options.<br><strong>Step 6:</strong> Click 'Answer key' (bottom left of question). Mark correct answer(s). Assign point value. Add answer feedback.<br><strong>Step 7:</strong> Repeat for all questions.<br><strong>Step 8:</strong> Preview (eye icon) to test. Send (top right) to share the quiz link."
