          example: "Example:\n'Paper Gantt: Days 1-10 across top. Tasks down left side. Coloured bars show each task span. Blue=Plan, Green=Design, Coral=Build, Gold=Review. Critical path: longest chain of dependent tasks. Total: 10 calendar days, 2.5 hrs/day average.'"
