          howToUse: "<strong>Step 1:</strong> Go to the YouTube video you want to embed.<br><strong>Step 2:</strong> Click 'Share' (below the video).<br><strong>Step 3:</strong> Click 'Embed' (you'll see HTML code appear).<br><strong>Step 4:</strong> Optional: Customize — uncheck 'Show player controls' or enable privacy-enhanced mode.<br><strong>Step 5:</strong> Copy the code (everything inside the text box).<br><strong>Step 6:</strong> In your website builder: Insert → Embed → Paste the code. The video appears on your page.<br><strong>Step 7:</strong> Resize by dragging the corners. Add a caption above or below."
