          solution: "Example:\n'MY PORTFOLIO STATEMENT:\n\n'I'm a 12-year-old student and creator from Pune. Over the past 10 months, I've learned to design in Canva, use AI tools for research and learning, produce videos, and build websites. My work focuses on turning ideas into visual stories — whether it's a poster, an infographic, a video, or a multi-page website. I'm most proud of my personal portfolio website, which I built from scratch and used to showcase everything I've learned. I'm just getting started.'\n\nWhy this works: It's short (4 sentences), specific (mentions tools and skills), honest ('just getting started'), and ends with forward momentum. It tells the visitor exactly what to expect from the portfolio below.'"
