          example: "Example celebration post:\n'Design: Instagram Square (1080×1080)\n\nBackground: Deep navy (from my brand kit)\n\nTop: 'EXPLORER LEVEL COMPLETE!' in bold white Outfit font, 48pt\n\nMiddle: My name 'ARJUN MEHTA' in gold (#FFD166), 36pt\n\nBelow name: 3 skills with icons:\n- 🎨 Design Thinking (paintbrush icon)\n- 🤖 AI Tools (robot icon)\n- 🌐 Web Development (globe icon)\n\nBottom: 'See my portfolio → arjuns-portfolio.wixsite.com' in white, 18pt\n\nAccent: Coral (#FF6B6B) underline below the title\n\nShared on: Family WhatsApp group, Instagram story, showed to my class teacher\n\nReactions: 15 likes on Instagram. Mom forwarded to 5 relatives. Teacher said: 'You should present this at assembly.'\n\nLesson: Sharing your achievement isn't bragging — it's inspiring others to start their own journey.'"
