          instruction: "Draw a 2-column list:\n\nColumn 1: Skills I Have (from Explorer level)\nColumn 2: Skills I Need (for Creator level and beyond)\n\nFor each skill in Column 2, write how you plan to develop it. This becomes your learning roadmap.",
